## Aggregations

### count

```ruby
# Count all records
Article.count

# Count with condition
Article.where(status: 'published').count

# Count distinct
Article.distinct.count(:user_id)

# Group count
Article.group(:status).count
# => {"draft"=>5, "published"=>10, "archived"=>2}
```

### sum, average, minimum, maximum

```ruby
# Sum
Article.sum(:views_count)
Article.where(status: 'published').sum(:views_count)

# Average
Article.average(:views_count)

# Minimum
Article.minimum(:created_at)

# Maximum
Article.maximum(:views_count)

# With group
Article.group(:category_id).sum(:views_count)
# => {1=>1000, 2=>500, 3=>750}
```

